===Pronunciation===
IPA: /ˈkoirɑ/

===Noun===
'''koira'''

#[[dog]]

====Synonyms====
*(''baby talk'') [[hauva]] ([[doggy]])
*(''old, poetic'') [[hurtta]] ([[hound dog]])
*(''derogatory'') [[rakki]], [[piski]] ([[mongrel]])

====Sayings====
#"''Se koira älähtää, johon kalikka kalahtaa''" ("it is the dog that gets hit, who yelps"; refers to belief that the person(s) protesting loudest are likely to be guilty)

